| Tool Name        | Use Case                     |
| ---------------- | ---------------------------- |
| Chrome DevTools  | Simulate different devices   |
| Bootstrap        | Prebuilt responsive grid     |
| Tailwind CSS     | Utility-first responsive CSS |
| Figma            | Design responsive UI mockups |
| Responsively App | Preview site in all sizes    |

